        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N. Y.</placeName>
                <date>17<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Augt./59</date>.</p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Pha</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>Rev. DrSir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">According to promise<lb/> I send you a paper “On Jewish<lb/>
                doctrines”. You will see<lb/> that the “Israelite.” does not<lb/> enter for much
                into this article.<lb/> The best way to refute fallacy<lb/> is to show facts.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I find however that the<lb/> paper grows under my hand<lb/> so that
                it must be decided.<lb/> This division I intend to take<lb/> place at page 6. where
                I have<lb/> marked my initials. The<lb/> whole will probably reach 12<lb/> pages of
                which I will send<lb/> you the remainder early</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>next week. I should like<lb/> it much if it were possible to let me see a proof
                before<lb/> you go to print. The same<lb/> morning I receive the proof<lb/> it shall
                go back.</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">Yours very respfy</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">M J Raphall</persName>
            </p>
